      <title>07 तृतीयोल्लासः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/kalpAntaram/dharmaH/nibandhaH/pratApa-rudra-sarasvatI-vilAsaH/vyavahArakANDaH/07_tRtIyollAsaH/</link>
