      <title>09 पञ्चमोल्लासः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/kalpAntaram/dharmaH/nibandhaH/pratApa-rudra-sarasvatI-vilAsaH/vyavahArakANDaH/09_panchamollAsaH/</link>
